nl_querry: Among the Artifact cards, which are black color and comes with foreign languague translation? Artifact card refers to originalType = 'Artifact'; black color refers to colors = 'B'; foreign language refers to language in foreign_data
llm_querry: SELECT c.name, fd.language FROM cards c JOIN foreign_data fd ON c.uuid = fd.uuid WHERE c.originalType = 'Artifact' AND c.colors = 'B' AND fd.language != 'English' ORDER BY c.name, fd.language;
gold_querry: SELECT DISTINCT T1.name FROM cards AS T1 INNER JOIN foreign_data AS T2 ON T1.uuid = T2.uuid WHERE T1.originalType = 'Artifact' AND T1.colors = 'B'
